AND WHICH ONE'S MEDIUM RARE.

00:04:42,949 --> 00:04:44,951
OR MAYBE YOU HAVE
A SPICY PIECE OF CHICKEN,

00:04:44,951 --> 00:04:47,754
BUT YOU WEREN'T PREPARED FOR IT,
AND IT LIGHTS YOU ON FIRE.

00:04:47,754 --> 00:04:50,123
