<i>KEVIN O'LEARY</i>
<i>HAS OFFERED $125,000</i>

00:39:44,215 --> 00:39:47,018
<i>FOR 51% OF THE COMPANY.</i>

00:39:47,018 --> 00:39:48,586
<i>BUT ROBERT HAS OUTBID HIM,</i>

00:39:48,586 --> 00:39:51,689
<i>OFFERING THE SAME AMOUNT</i>
<i>FOR ONLY 40% OF THE COMPANY.</i>

00:39:51,689 --> 00:39:53,925
WHAT'S YOUR‐‐
WHAT'S YOUR PLAN?

00:39:53,925 --> 00:39:56,227
WAIT, WAIT, WAIT, WAIT, WAIT.
WAIT, WAIT. HE'S NEVER, EVER‐‐

00:39:56,227 --> 00:39:58,229
I'VE DONE WHAT I'VE
JUST DESCRIBED TO YOU

00:39:58,229 --> 00:40:00,331
A HUNDRED TIMES, AND THE PROOF
IS IN THE PUDDING.

00:40:00,331 --> 00:40:03,101
MY ONLY PROBLEM IS THAT
I NEED‐‐I NEED OWNERSHIP.

00:40:03,101 --> 00:40:05,336
I DON'T WANT OWNERSHIP.

00:40:05,336 --> 00:40:08,006
WHAT I WANT IS THE ABILITY
TO CLOSE.
WITH 51%.

