00:41:50,641 --> 00:41:53,678
FOR 51% OF THE COMPANY.

00:41:53,678 --> 00:41:57,115
AND YOU KNOW
<i>WHY</i> IT HAS TO BE 51%.

00:41:57,115 --> 00:41:59,784
THAT'S THE OFFER.
WHAT ARE YOU GOING TO DO?

00:41:59,784 --> 00:42:03,821
<i>THE SHARKS HAVE OFFERED SAWYER</i>
<i>$175,000 MORE</i>

00:42:03,821 --> 00:42:05,823
<i>THAN WHAT HE CAME IN SEEKING,</i>

00:42:05,823 --> 00:42:10,194
