YEAH. (laughs)
(laughs)

00:42:42,660 --> 00:42:44,495
IT'S A GREAT DEAL
FOR MY COMMUNITY,

00:42:44,495 --> 00:42:46,497
AND IT'S FOR YOU,
BLOOMFIELD, INDIANA.

00:42:46,497 --> 00:42:48,833
